feat(lifecycle): add nested collapsible subsections in stage content

Builds nested `.stage-subsection` blocks from `h3-h6` headings in
`applyStageSubsections()` inside `src/js/renderer.ts` using a stack to
preserve heading hierarchy, defaulting each subsection to `collapsed`,
and applies it through `applyLifecycleSubsections()`. Adds subsection
header toggle handling in `initStageToggle()` in `src/js/main.ts` and
resets all subsections to collapsed (including
`stage-subsection-toggle-icon`) whenever a stage is expanded. Introduces
`.stage-subsection*` styles in `src/styles/main.css` and switches
expand/collapse selectors to direct-child `>` rules to prevent parent
expansion from auto-expanding nested content.
